# Nexa Web — Project Conventions

Follow these rules for all work in this repository. Human-readable docs: `docs/AI_RULES.md` (master), `docs/PROJECT_STRUCTURE.md`, `docs/LIBRARIES_AND_CONSTRAINTS.md`.

## Libraries

Full reference: `docs/LIBRARIES_AND_CONSTRAINTS.md` and `docs/AI_RULES.md`. Prefer libraries already wired in the feature you touch; do not add new UI frameworks.

| Category | Package | Use in nexa-web |
|----------|---------|-----------------|
| Framework | `@angular/*` ^21.2 | Standalone app; `bootstrapApplication`; `@angular/build:application` |
| CDK | `@angular/cdk` | Available; use only if existing patterns do |
| State | `@ngrx/store`, `@ngrx/effects` ^21 | **Only** `customers/` and `wallets/` `state/` |
| Auth | `@auth0/auth0-angular` | Login, guards, HTTP token interceptor for `environemnt.apiUrl/*` |
| UI | `primeng`, `primeicons`, `@primeuix/themes` | Primary components; theme via `appThemePreset` in `ng-prime.theme.ts` |
| CSS | `tailwindcss`, `@tailwindcss/postcss`, `@tailwindcss/typography` | Global utilities in templates; entry `src/styles/styles.scss` |
| i18n | `@ngx-translate/core`, `@ngx-translate/http-loader` | Runtime strings: `src/assets/i18n/en.json`; separate from `@angular/localize` polyfill |
| Icons | `@ng-icons/core`, `@ng-icons/heroicons`, `@ng-icons/feather-icons`, `lucide-angular` | Import per component |
| Forms / phone | `google-libphonenumber`, `libphonenumber-js` | `shared/components/phone-input` validator |
| Forms / phone | `ngx-intl-tel-input` | In package.json; prefer custom `PhoneInput` unless extending tel UX |
| Payments | `@stripe/stripe-js` | `features/banks/services/stripe.service.ts` |
| KYC | ComplyCube (global CSS/JS in `angular.json`) | `features/onboarding/services/comply-cube.service.ts` |
| Bootstrap | `ngx-bootstrap` | **Not referenced in `src/`** — do not introduce without explicit request |
| RxJS | `rxjs` ~7.8 | Services, effects, guards |
| Test (dev) | `vitest`, `@analogjs/vite-plugin-angular`, `@testing-library/angular`, `jsdom` | `ng test`; `vitest-base.config.ts`, `src/test-setup.ts` |

## Constraints

**TypeScript** (`tsconfig.json`): `strict: true`, `strictNullChecks`, `strictTemplates`; `strictPropertyInitialization: false`; `noImplicitOverride`, `noImplicitReturns`, `noFallthroughCasesInSwitch`; `target: ES2022`, `module: preserve`

**Angular** (`angular.json`): prefix `app`; default style `scss`; production budgets — initial 500kB warn / 1MB error, component styles 4kB / 8kB; polyfill `@angular/localize/init` (build-time i18n, not ngx-translate)

**Formatting** (`.prettierrc`, `.editorconfig`): 2 spaces, UTF-8, final newline, single quotes (TS); Prettier `printWidth: 80`, `trailingComma: all`, `singleAttributePerLine: true`, Angular HTML parser

**Architecture:** standalone components only (no NgModules); feature-first under `src/app/features/`; NgRx only customers + wallets; wallets no routes (embed via containers); HTTP `environemnt.apiUrl` + `errorHandlerInterceptorFn` + `authHttpInterceptorFn`; Auth0 + `customerGuardFn` on PublicLayout routes; minimal diffs; preserve known typos unless asked

**Do not add** (unless user requests): new state libs, NgModules, alternate CSS frameworks, fixing duplicate `provideHttpClient()` in `app.config.ts`

## Folder structure (summary)

See `docs/PROJECT_STRUCTURE.md` for the full tree. Quick map:

```
src/app/
  features/{name}/     # auth, customers, wallets, onboarding, transfers, banks, landing
  core/ shared/ layouts/ components/
```

## Project structure (detailed)

### Repository root

```
nexa-web/
├── angular.json, package.json, tsconfig*.json, vitest-base.config.ts
├── .prettierrc, .editorconfig, .cursor/rules/nexa-web.mdc
├── public/                    # static assets
├── docs/PROJECT_STRUCTURE.md  # full structure reference
└── src/
    ├── main.ts                # bootstrapApplication(App, appConfig)
    ├── test-setup.ts
    ├── app/                   # application code
    ├── assets/                # i18n, complycube css/js
    ├── environments/          # environemnt.ts
    ├── styles/                # Tailwind + theme partials
    └── testing/               # dom-helpers, ng-prime-test utilities, mocks
```

### `src/app/` shell

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `app.ts` | Root: RouterOutlet, RoutingGlobalLoader, DataLoaderError |
| `app.config.ts` | All provide* (HTTP, Auth0, PrimeNG, translate, NgRx, features) |
| `app.routes.ts` | Wildcard `**` → NotFound only |
| `ng-prime.theme.ts` | Lara + emerald preset |
| `components/` | not-found, routing-global-loader |
| `layouts/auth-layout/` | `/auth`, `/onboarding` |
| `layouts/public-layout/` | `/`, `/customer`, `/transfers`, `/banks` (+ public-navbar) |

### Core and shared

```
core/
